<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Psychology</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">12</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 187</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Design Thinking</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2+0+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">05.04.2024</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Design Thinking trainings consist of five main parts; empathy, defining the problem, generating ideas, modelling and testing. In these parts, interaction with the environment and people is primarily important.
Design-oriented thinking, which is a solution-oriented thinking method, has a structure that makes the participants apply all five stages in a practical way at the point of assimilating the environment and environment of the participants, identifying the needs correctly and developing designs.
One of the most important features of the method is that it can be easily integrated into every sector and can be easily grasped and applied by people of all ages and educational levels.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=325875&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Psychology</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">12</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 188</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Startup Design with Design Thinking</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2+0+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">05.04.2024</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">To a large extent, design is about creating the conditions that allow startups to grow, flourish and transform in an environment of uncertainty and change. In other words, the best startups are those that can approach problems in a new and systematic way, focusing on actions rather than plans and predictions. Smart startups combine design and strategy and use opportunities in an uncertain and unpredictable world to manage growth. This course will help you to identify which tools to use when and how to use them in order to design and realise a smart enterprise and make the right decisions.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=325876&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Psychology</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">12</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 189</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Forensic Informatics</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2+0+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">05.04.2024</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Within the scope of the course, it is aimed to explain the basic concepts of Forensic Informatics and to inform those who will work in this field and who want to specialise in this field, to get basic information and methodologies and to learn applications. Introduction to Forensic Informatics and basic concepts, stages of Forensic Informatics, Cyber crimes, Cyber violence, Cyber attacks and methods, examination of new technologies in terms of KVKK and GDPR, adoption of Cyber Security and National Cyber Security awareness, multidisciplinary approach and working algorithms in forensic sciences will be examined in the course.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=325877&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Psychology</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">12</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 190</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Philosophy of Cinema</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2+0+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">05.04.2024</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Classic films will be analysed philosophically. At the same time, philosophical themed films will be evaluated.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=325878&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Psychology</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">12</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 191</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Business Analysis</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2+0+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">05.04.2024</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Principles and methods of international business analysis</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=325879&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Psychology</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">12</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 204</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Power and Inequality</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2+0+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">05.04.2024</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">The course will analyze main theories of social stratification and social inequality. It will also focus on global stratification, as well as racial and gender inequalities.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=325714&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Psychology</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">12</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 208</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">History of Thought</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2+0+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">05.04.2024</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Presenting examples from the history of human thought/philosophy starting from the Ancient Greek Thought extending to 20th century Phenomenology</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=325716&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Psychology</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">12</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 209</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Musics of The World’s Cultures</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2+0+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">05.04.2024</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Introduction of world music cultures and examination of musical traditions.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=325704&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Psychology</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">12</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 210</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Cultural Memory and Photographs</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2+0+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">05.04.2024</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">In recent days memory has become one of the mostly debated issues in social sciences and everyday life. Society and people have become more interested in the past. There are movies, television series and books that are trying to create a connection between the past and present. On the other side photographs are the most important companions in our lives from the day we were born. In this cultural context family photographs became a carrier of cultural memory. This lecture is going to be an introduction to cultural memory and photograph within an interdisciplinary perspective. Both of the topics will be introduced independently and their relation will be discussed critically with the questions and topics such as; how and why we remember?, why we forget?, nostalgic remembering, what a photograph record, ‘reading’ reflections of a photograph.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=325703&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Psychology</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">12</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 211</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Understanding Everday Life Practices of Turkey</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2+0+0</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">05.04.2024</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Everyone of us has daily practices in our lifes such as reading
newspapers, watching tv shows, walking through the city or
going to malls. During the semester we are going to understand
and discuss the meaning of our habits. Why do we have daily
routines? Are we choosing our daily habits? How does the
culture of everyday life in Turkey change? We are going to
discuss such questions within the semester with the help of
selected articles, visual materials- photographs, advertisementsand
our own daily routines.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=325735&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">OK</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String"></Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Psychology</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">12</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 212</Data></Cell>
