<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Throughout the lessons, various gender approaches in the literature will be discussed from different perspectives, and in the following processes, students will be asked to choose a material that will enable them to examine the gender roles they encounter in the media in their daily lives. For example, they will be expected to discuss an outdoor visual about breast cancer awareness, which will address the issue of femininity, or prostate cancer awareness, which will address the issue of masculinity.</Data></Cell>
