<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Psychology</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">12</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 150</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Historical Continuity from the Ottoman to the Republic</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Gain information about the Ottoman Empire that ruled before the Republic of Turkey, comprehend the transition process from Ottoman to Republic. learn the social and cultural heritage that was transferred from the Ottoman Empire to the Republic, evaluate the historical continuity phenomena from the Ottoman Empire to the Republic, establish a connection between the past and the present and be able to make comment on the topics.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=325724&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Psychology</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">12</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 151</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Digital Photography and Photo Processing Techniques</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Define photography, master the process of photography from film to digital, and establish its historical context, understand how the camera works and how it records.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=325725&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Psychology</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">12</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 151</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Digital Photography and Photo Processing Techniques</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">2</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Explain the concept of accurate exposure within the framework of photosensitive surface, photosensitivity, light measurement and light qualities, explain alternative correct exposures in terms of clear depth of field and recording movement.</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=325725&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Psychology</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">12</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">ACU 151</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Digital Photography and Photo Processing Techniques</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Explain the technological possibilities offered in the camera, the process of photographic film and printing, and digital photography technology, define general image editing rules</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">https://obs.acibadem.edu.tr/oibs/bologna/progCourseDetails.aspx?curCourse=325725&amp;lang=en</Data></Cell>
</Row>
<Row>
