<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">20th Century Political and Social History</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">8</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">Changing Balancesat the End-of-war. Institutions of Cold War-era. Establishment of the United Nations. The Establishment Of Israel. Israel-Arab bloc wars in the Middle East.</Data></Cell>
