<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">20th Century Political and Social History</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">9</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">1950-1968: the process of transition to a welfare society. Revolution in Cuba. The Start Of The Vietnam War.</Data></Cell>
