<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">3</Data></Cell>
<Cell ss:StyleID="Text"><Data ss:Type="String">The horror of science: Frankenstein (1930’s)
Reading: Picart, Caroline. “Visualizing the Monstrous in Frankensteinn Films.” (2000)
